<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .alert-box {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .button-cancel { background-color: #dc3545; color: white; }
    .button-secure { background-color: #28a745; color: white; }
    .warning { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>⚠️ SECURITY ALERT</h2>
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <strong>🚨 Important Security Notice</strong><br><br>
      A request has been made to change your email to: <strong>{{newEmail}}</strong>
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>⏰ Request time:</strong> {{requestTime}}</p>
    
    <p class="warning">⚠️ <strong>If you did NOT make this request, your account may be compromised!</strong></p>
    
    <p><strong>Choose an action:</strong></p>
    <a href="{{revokeUrl}}" class="button button-cancel">❌ Cancel Request</a>
    <a href="{{secureUrl}}" class="button button-secure">🔒 Secure My Account</a>
    
    <p>If you did make this request, please ignore this email and proceed with the verification code sent to your new email address.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>{{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>